Looks like one of the tests asserts that the segment download url should not change if CRC is the same.

@Jackie-Jiang : do you have context about it?

https://github.com/apache/pinot/blob/be496bc763ac94660098c3a9e1f4a75167731789/pinot-controller/src/test/java/org/apache/pinot/controller/api/upload/ZKOperatorTest.java#L295-L299

@FranMorilloAWS I wonder if setting completion mode to `DOWNLOAD` is causing this issue. 
any particular reason why you are using this config?

```
"completionConfig": {
"completionMode": "DOWNLOAD"
}
```
